{"tid":1821457,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"新香港的模範中學 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-01-12T10:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T10:54:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3712a5050b4c7f94c133a3c02a172101fa4b6248","tid":1821457,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:04:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200112/20841896/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F20841896%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXdw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=a110f747\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F20841896%2F&h=b997172e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200112/20841896/</a><br />\n<br />\n新香港的模範中學 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200112/large/1578735894_801c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200112%2Flarge%2F1578735894_801c.jpg&h=e9bc4a48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月十三日，新蒲崗有中學生趁午飯時間，上街參與反暴政集會，不料被訓導教師知悉，待他們回到學校，當眾痛斥：「反政府者破壞社會穩定，是否要香港像烏克蘭那樣動蕩不安？我有的是錢，可以無懼，但不忍香港變成這個樣子。香港警隊質素天下第一，反政府者竟然主張解散，實在莫名其妙。」這位富可驕人女教師原來供職可立中學。<br />\n<br />\n二零零四年，可立有中文教師獻「詩」與偽教育統籌局秘書長范椒芬，說什麼「椒語安有辛辣意，芬馥腔調撫瑤琴」等，八句頭八字生拼硬湊出「羅范椒芬功在教苑」的奇文。是這家號稱儒釋道合流的中學，前有詩翁，後有富婆，洵足令孔子厚顏，佛祖失色，老君低首。<br />\n<br />\n最近，偽教育局一再頒令「禁止政治滲入校園」，並嚴懲教師發表「偏頗政治言論」者，目前至少已有三十位教師遭清算，職位料將不保。但是，教師誇譽黑警，歌頌偽長官，膜拜習近平，則一定不是「政治」；能使學生步亦步，趨亦趨，則更應旌表。可立中學詩翁富婆之流，將有大用，自可必也。<br />\n<br />\n至於不識時務的教師、校長，則須究治不貸，連死者都要鞭屍。去年十一月，香港華人永遠墳場故北京大學校長蔡元培之墓，就被人搗毀，搗毀者還在網上有恃無恐說：「只要打電話給我，我即自首。」而香港黑警接到墳場當局報案，果然說：「這只是財物損失，並非刑事案件。」 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"5e4864eaf62835569c3923bd3f2cf72ad72a2cf2","tid":1821457,"uid":96095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d74b30bc1965cda0e2c3fb160b5da99f64479a","tid":1821457,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"日期：2020年1月13日 星期一<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">鰂魚涌:香港保險㒰人職工會街站</span><br />\n時間 ： 1200-1500<br />\n地點 ：太古坊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">維園:香港制藥及醫療儀器業職工總會街站</span><br />\n時間 ： 1230-1400<br />\n地點 ：維園圓形噴水池<br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">中環:119天下制裁大遊行</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月19日 星期日<br />\n時間 ： 1500<br />\n地點 ：遮打道 至 銅鑼灣SOGO<br />\n(*不反對通知書申請中)"},{"pid":"ff95f77bf70406d8657cf2d3d0d95fc51d6c380a","tid":1821457,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:08:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b768cc1490e6e3048ecac503a571822aee325c2","tid":1821457,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"祝教畜死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90df7e9d9073671d1fd16b69013bdbf36d1ba0e0","tid":1821457,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"所有畜牲死全家"},{"pid":"87636cde3805d72aeed9428bc5a487792a83e775","tid":1821457,"uid":342786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"唔通烏克蘭比外敵俄羅斯入侵要跪底唔反抗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}